#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:1
msgid "SSH API"
msgstr "SSH API"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:3
msgid ""
"SSH connection, remote execution, and file transfer helpers are available "
"under `ptool.ssh` and `p.ssh`."
msgstr "SSH 连接、远程执行和文件传输辅助能力位于 `ptool.ssh` 和 `p.ssh` 下。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:5
msgid "ptool.ssh.connect"
msgstr "ptool.ssh.connect"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:7
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:7"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:9
msgid ""
"`ptool.ssh.connect(target_or_options)` prepares an SSH connection handle "
"backed by the system `ssh` command and returns a `Connection` object."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.ssh.connect(target_or_options)` 会准备一个由系统 `ssh` 命令驱动的 SSH "
"连接句柄，并返回一个 `Connection` 对象。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:12
msgid "`ssh` must be available on `PATH`."
msgstr "运行环境中必须能在 `PATH` 中找到 `ssh`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:14
msgid "Arguments:"
msgstr "参数："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:16
msgid "`target_or_options` (string|table, required):"
msgstr "`target_or_options`（string|table，必填）："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:16
msgid "When a string is provided, it is treated as an SSH target."
msgstr "传入字符串时，会被视为 SSH target。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:16
msgid "When a table is provided, it currently supports:"
msgstr "传入 table 时，目前支持："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:16
msgid ""
"`target` (string, optional): SSH target string such as `"
"\"deploy@example.com\"` or `\"deploy@example.com:2222\"`."
msgstr ""
"`target`（string，可选）：SSH target 字符串，例如 `\"deploy@example.com\"` 或"
" `\"deploy@example.com:2222\"`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:16
msgid "`host` (string, optional): Hostname or IP address."
msgstr "`host`（string，可选）：主机名或 IP 地址。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:16
msgid ""
"`user` (string, optional): SSH username. Defaults to `$USER`, or `\"root\"` "
"if `$USER` is unavailable."
msgstr "`user`（string，可选）：SSH 用户名。默认取 `$USER`；如果 `$USER` 不可用，则默"
"认为 `\"root\"`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:16
msgid "`port` (integer, optional): SSH port. Defaults to `22`."
msgstr "`port`（integer，可选）：SSH 端口。默认值为 `22`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:16
msgid "`auth` (table, optional): Authentication settings."
msgstr "`auth`（table，可选）：认证设置。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:16
msgid "`host_key` (table, optional): Host key verification settings."
msgstr "`host_key`（table，可选）：主机密钥校验设置。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:16
msgid ""
"`connect_timeout_ms` (integer, optional): Timeout in milliseconds. Defaults "
"to `10000`."
msgstr "`connect_timeout_ms`（integer，可选）：超时时间（毫秒）。默认值为 `10000`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:16
msgid ""
"`keepalive_interval_ms` (integer, optional): Keepalive interval in "
"milliseconds."
msgstr "`keepalive_interval_ms`（integer，可选）：keepalive 间隔（毫秒）。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:32
msgid "Supported target string examples:"
msgstr "支持的 target 字符串示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:40
msgid "`auth` fields:"
msgstr "`auth` 字段："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:42
msgid "`private_key_file` (string, optional): Path to a private key file."
msgstr "`private_key_file`（string，可选）：私钥文件路径。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:43
msgid ""
"`private_key_passphrase` (string, optional): Passphrase for the private key. "
"This is currently not supported."
msgstr "`private_key_passphrase`（string，可选）：私钥口令。目前不支持。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:45
msgid ""
"`password` (string, optional): Password-based authentication. This is "
"currently not supported."
msgstr "`password`（string，可选）：密码认证所用的密码。目前不支持。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:48
msgid "Authentication behavior:"
msgstr "认证行为："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:50
msgid ""
"If `auth.private_key_file` is provided, `ptool` invokes `ssh` with that key "
"via `-i` and also sets `IdentitiesOnly=yes`."
msgstr ""
"如果提供了 `auth.private_key_file`，`ptool` 会通过 `-i` 将该私钥传给 `ssh`，"
"并同时设置 `IdentitiesOnly=yes`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:52
msgid ""
"If `auth.private_key_passphrase` or `auth.password` is provided, "
"`ptool.ssh.connect(...)` fails because this API does not pass those secrets "
"to the system `ssh` command."
msgstr ""
"如果提供了 `auth.private_key_passphrase` 或 `auth.password`， "
"`ptool.ssh.connect(...)` 会失败，因为该 API 不会把这些密钥材料直接传给 系统 "
"`ssh` 命令。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:55
msgid ""
"Otherwise, authentication is delegated to the local OpenSSH setup, including "
"settings and mechanisms such as `IdentityFile`, `ProxyJump`, `ProxyCommand`, "
"`ssh-agent`, and certificates."
msgstr ""
"否则，认证完全交给本机 OpenSSH 配置处理，包括 `IdentityFile`、 `ProxyJump`、"
"`ProxyCommand`、`ssh-agent` 和证书等机制。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:58
msgid ""
"Relative key paths are resolved from the current `ptool` runtime directory, "
"so they follow `ptool.cd(...)`."
msgstr "相对私钥路径会从当前 `ptool` 运行时目录解析，因此会受到 `ptool.cd(...)` 的影"
"响。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:60
msgid "`~` and `~/...` are expanded in key paths."
msgstr "私钥路径中的 `~` 和 `~/...` 会被展开。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:62
msgid "`host_key` fields:"
msgstr "`host_key` 字段："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:64
msgid ""
"`verify` (string, optional): Host key verification mode. Supported values:"
msgstr "`verify`（string，可选）：主机密钥校验模式。支持："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:64
msgid "`\"known_hosts\"`: Verify against a known_hosts file (default)."
msgstr "`\"known_hosts\"`：根据 known_hosts 文件校验（默认）。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:64
msgid "`\"ignore\"`: Skip host key verification."
msgstr "`\"ignore\"`：跳过主机密钥校验。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:67
msgid ""
"`known_hosts_file` (string, optional): Path to a known_hosts file. Used only "
"when `verify = \"known_hosts\"`."
msgstr ""
"`known_hosts_file`（string，可选）：known_hosts 文件路径。仅在 `verify = "
"\"known_hosts\"` 时使用。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:70
msgid "Host key behavior:"
msgstr "主机密钥行为："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:72
msgid ""
"If `verify = \"ignore\"`, `ptool` invokes `ssh` with "
"`StrictHostKeyChecking=no` and `UserKnownHostsFile=/dev/null`."
msgstr ""
"如果 `verify = \"ignore\"`，`ptool` 会给 `ssh` 传入 "
"`StrictHostKeyChecking=no` 和 `UserKnownHostsFile=/dev/null`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:74
msgid ""
"If `verify = \"known_hosts\"` and `known_hosts_file` is provided, `ptool` "
"invokes `ssh` with `StrictHostKeyChecking=yes` and that `UserKnownHostsFile`."
msgstr ""
"如果 `verify = \"known_hosts\"` 且提供了 `known_hosts_file`，`ptool` 会给 "
"`ssh` 传入 `StrictHostKeyChecking=yes`，并设置对应的 `UserKnownHostsFile`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:77
msgid ""
"If `verify = \"known_hosts\"` and `known_hosts_file` is omitted, or when "
"`host_key` is omitted entirely, host key handling is delegated to the local "
"OpenSSH configuration and defaults."
msgstr ""
"如果 `verify = \"known_hosts\"` 但省略了 `known_hosts_file`，或者整个 "
"`host_key` 都被省略，则主机密钥处理交给本机 OpenSSH 配置和默认行为。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:80
msgid ""
"Relative `known_hosts_file` paths are resolved from the current `ptool` "
"runtime directory."
msgstr "相对 `known_hosts_file` 路径会从当前 `ptool` 运行时目录解析。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:82
msgid "`~` and `~/...` are expanded in `known_hosts_file`."
msgstr "`known_hosts_file` 中的 `~` 和 `~/...` 会被展开。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:83
msgid ""
"When `known_hosts_file` is provided explicitly, it overrides the default "
"`UserKnownHostsFile` used by the local `ssh` command for this connection."
msgstr ""
"当显式提供 `known_hosts_file` 时，它会覆盖本次连接中本机 `ssh` 命令默认 使用"
"的 `UserKnownHostsFile`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:86
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:86"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:102
msgid "Connection"
msgstr "Connection"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:104
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:104"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:106
msgid ""
"`Connection` represents an OpenSSH-backed connection handle returned by "
"`ptool.ssh.connect()`."
msgstr "`Connection` 表示由 `ptool.ssh.connect()` 返回的、基于 OpenSSH 的连接句柄。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:109
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:109"
msgid "It is implemented as a Lua userdata."
msgstr "它实现为 Lua userdata。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:111
msgid "Fields and methods:"
msgstr "字段和方法："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:113
msgid "Fields:"
msgstr "字段："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:113
msgid "`conn.host` (string)"
msgstr "`conn.host`（string）"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/ssh.md:113
